fields.name: Crayola Broad Line Markers, 10 Classic Colors
fields.description: Create in rich colors with this this 10 Count Crayola Broad Line Marker Set. The nontoxic Markers in classic colors are perfect for home art supplies, and much more. Crayola, not just for kids express your art with these bold colors and your own imagination!

fields.name: Staedtler Double-Ended Lettering Brush Pens Set of 12
fields.description:
Set of 12 Double-ended Lettering Pens from Staedtler. Featuring a fine tip at one end and a brush at the other, they're ideal for both lettering and modern calligraphy as well as fine detailing and illustration.

The line width with the fine tip varies between 0.5mm and 0.8mm, while the brush varies from 1mm to 6mm.

fields.name: Sharpie Metallic Permanent Marker Assorted Set of 3
fields.description:
Sharpie is the original and iconic marker. It contains quick-drying water-resistant ink that permanently marks most surfaces including glass, metal, photos, foil and most plastics. Resilient tip resists abrasion; tough polypropylene barrel stands up to almost anything.

Set contains 3 Metallic Markers in gold, silver and bronze.

fields.name: Tombow Dual Brush Pens, Primary Pallette, 10 Pen Set
fields.description:
Tombow Dual Brush Pens, Primary Pallette, 56167, 10 Pen Set. Set of 9 colors with flexible brush tip and fine tip in one marker and 1 blender pen. Brush tip works like a paintbrush to create fine, medium or bold strokes; fine tip gives consistent lines. 

The water based ink is blendable and the resilient nylon brush retains its point stroke after stroke. Dual brush pens are ideal for fine art and illustrations and are perfect for every artists masterpiece. Colors in set are: Process Yellow, Pink Rose-Manga, Scarlet, Sap Green, Cyan, Imperial Purple, Crimson, Brown and Black.

fields.name: Faber-Castell Pitt Artist Pen Wallet of 8 (Black)
fields.description:
The Faber-Castell Pitt Pen is a highly-regarded artists' drawing pen, suitable for sketches, studies and ink drawings. Each pen features highly light-fast, waterproof drawing ink for maximum, long-lasting impact.  

This wallet of eight black Pitt pens comes in varying nib sizes: XS (0.1mm), S (0.3mm), F (0.5mm), M (0.7mm), B (1-5mm), SC (1-3mm), SB (0.5-5mm) & 1.5 (1.5mm).

fields.name: Giotto Decor Pens
fields.description:
Fabulous selection of multi-purpose fibre pens. Suitable for use on almost any surface including wood, stone, porcelain and plastic. 

Water-based and comes in 12 assorted bright colours.

fields.name: Pentel Pocket Brush Pen
fields.description:
Bring the elegance of Asian calligraphy to your artwork and writing. This high-quality, smooth-writing brush pen from Pentel lets the artist vary line widths from thick to thin, achieving many beautiful effects. The ink is waterproof once fully dry, and is safe for use with watercolors.

The pen refills conveniently with cartridges, and two black ink cartridges are included.

fields.name: Winsor & Newton ProMarker Neon (Set of 6)
fields.description:
Highly pigmented and lightfast, Winsor & Newton Neon colours are perfect for adding vibrant highlights to art and design work. This set includes six fluorescent colours: Electric Pink, Glowing Green, Luminous Yellow, Radiant Orange, Spark Red and Volt Blue.

Featuring a fine tip at one end and a medium bullet nib at the other, the Winsor & Newton Neon allows a variety of line widths to be created. These marker pens contain water-based ink, which is both lightfast and acid free, ensuring long-lasting results.

fields.name: Winsor & Newton ProMarker Metallic (Set of 6)
fields.description:
Expert, versatile and boasting an unrivalled colour spectrum, the Winsor & Newton ProMarker is a must-have, professional quality addition to your marker collection. This set includes six metallic colours: Violet, Blue, Green, Silver, Gold and Red Gold.


Each marker is twin-tipped, with a broad chisel nib and fine bullet nib. These nibs are of a very high quality to ensure consistent, streak-free coverage. All ProMarkers are blend-friendly and contain malleable, alcohol-based, translucent ink.

The set is made up of six black fineliners, one of each of the following sizes: 0.20mm, 0.25mm, 0.30mm, 0.35mm, 0.45mm, 0.50mm

A high quality white 260gsm hammer effect A5 card that has excellent qualities for custom invites. This is a very popular A5 white paper. It has a good feel of quality and works well in any project where a good strength paper weight is essential.

This card is single sided, perfect for writing/printing on the inside.   Always check your printer can except 260gsm paper before purchase.

This package contains three professional brush pens with fine medium and bold tips.

fields.name: Prismacolor Premier Illustration Art Markers Assorted Tip Markers
fields.description:
Includes five fine point markers (005, 01, 03, 05 and 08), a brush tip marker and a chisel tip marker.

Does it ever seem like you just can't find that lovely, fine-point black pen that you want to use for doodling, writing out fancy cards, or pen-and-ink drawings? Perfect for all of those things, these sets of good-quality markers will give you the fine nib sizes you want to create the finest drawings or hand lettering. The archival-quality ink is a lovely deep black but does not bleed through paper, and it is smear resistant when dry.
